{"tid":1418421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【長期置頂】香城Online武力指引（初版）","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T19:06:03.000Z","uid":298639,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9cc71bf29464d484b1ae6a9b6dcdf35d4fe0c872","tid":1418421,"uid":298639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:40:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>抗爭者以暴力制衡國家暴力</strong></span>呢個係我地目前<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>行動方向</strong></span>，而我地目前<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>訴求方向</strong></span>簡而言之係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「重建屬於民主社會既正確秩序」</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">，話比政府知</span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「政府應該畏懼自己既人民，而唔係人民畏懼政府」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">鑑於近日發夢留意到既事，同之後睇番唔同資訊得出既概括局面，我地內部明顯存在何謂<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「合理武力」</span></span></strong>既分歧，可以</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無大台</span></strong></span>，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「欲建立秩序之先必須有秩序化」</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">既傾向，為左之後既一連串行動可以更加<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行之有效</span></strong></span>，而目前對武力指引清晰既討論甚少，所以本人係到先拋磚引玉，有咩唔岩聽可以屌下，比下意見再作修改。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>初版指引如下：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>角色：勇武、和理非；對手：政府、狗、黑社會（持械、揸車惡意沖防線者當係）、非尋常市民（指罵或影相者當係，另分遠近）</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>勇武VS政府</strong></span>（<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">魔攻、物攻</span></span></strong>，另建議Set好路障就快決定幾時唔再放車，今日北角搬黎搬去玩自己人）</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非VS政府</span></strong>（<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不合作、支援勇武、傳話、散物資</span></strong></span>、休息可以但唔好長時間出黎鳩坐）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武VS狗</span></strong>（<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">魔攻、物攻</span></span></strong>，ps千萬<strong>唔好落單</strong>，落單狗自己識做啦）</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非VS狗</span></strong>（<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心理口號攻勢</span></span></strong>，再重覆<strong>千唔萬好落單</strong>）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武VS黑社會</span></strong>（<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">物攻</span></span></strong>，持械者一定要打，朋友發夢同我講佢好撚後悔心軟無打到佢仆街；沖路者架車就識做啦，落左車就建議綁索帶羞辱下佢，唔好打太重）</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非VS持械黑社會</span></strong>（自己人少既話極速走住叫救命，人多就睇定D視乎情況唔好怯）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武+和理非VS非尋常市民</span></strong>（呢到要統一武力）<br />\n<br />\nVS<strong>上方影相市民</strong>（唔洗理，咁遠自己醒目<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">black boc</span></strong>真係驚春咩）<br />\n<br />\nVS<strong>近處影相市民</strong>（先<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>友善勸喻</strong></span>，但如果佢屌你老母就<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一齊屌番佢</span></strong>）<br />\n<br />\nVS<strong>指罵市民</strong>（建議背天崎呢句作回應：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「從來，令到社會亂既只有當權者，唔係反抗者。 社會要反思既係，點解會有咁大反抗。 點解你地會指責一啲被壓迫既人，而唔去指責壓迫人既政權？」</strong></span>，如果有記者訪問都可以用呢句統一口徑，令呢個論點深入民心，將矛頭指番去政府）<br />\n<br />\nVS<strong>高空扔野市民</strong>（<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>照到佢仆街</strong></span>，同時要保護自己）<br />\n<br />\n初稿如上<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日辛苦大家，不要放棄，<strong>希望有日我地可以除低口罩係煲底相擁</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">若然政府最後都無視我地既訴求，不排除以後<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">If we burn you burn with us</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我係P牌仔會自屌10次</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"47f03cf085fa2126b170e3843229f88185f0da4d","tid":1418421,"uid":298639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:41:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>我係P牌仔對唔住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"039b9b8c548b702935712d72fc226e86bdc1b6ef","tid":1418421,"uid":298639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:41:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>我係P牌仔對唔住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0082d7ef908dd7e283fb848c115ad4bdc18e28f2","tid":1418421,"uid":298639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:41:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>我係P牌仔對唔住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"efdfb03ee37a29b0c3991d39d4cd4740ef94809a","tid":1418421,"uid":298639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:41:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>我係P牌仔對唔住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c7b38acad1ecae86be9468d5304b702f471ffcf4","tid":1418421,"uid":298639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:42:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>我係P牌仔對唔住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4a501cb21a5c1bbc5814fa734f3f75292c41894c","tid":1418421,"uid":298639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply